								<div id="hs_cos_wrapper_module_1539260109847467_" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_rich_text" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="inline_rich_text" data-hs-cos-field="wysiwyg"><h2>Have you ever considered the amount of more important tasks your front desk resources could be focusing on instead of manually tracking the day's visitors?</h2>
									<p><strong>Are you missing information:<span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}">&nbsp;</span></strong><span></span></p>
									<ul>
										<li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="2" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span><span>Who is coming?</span></span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}">&nbsp;</span></li>
										<li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="2" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span><span>When your visitors are coming?</span></span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}">&nbsp;</span></li>
										<li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="2" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span><span>Where they need to go?</span></span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}">&nbsp;</span></li>
										<li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="2" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span><span>Who they will be meeting with?</span></span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}">&nbsp;</span></li>
										<li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="2" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span><span>How long they will be in your office?</span></span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}">&nbsp;</span></li>
									</ul>
									<p><span><span>What is more, all the tedious<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>task<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>like registration of guests, guest logging, NDA signing, printing of guests passes / name tags and notifications to the host are done manually at your front<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>desk?&nbsp;</span></span><span><span>In</span></span><span><span><span>&nbsp;</span>this<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>eBook</span></span><span><span><span>&nbsp;</span>you'll learn how to optimize all of these processes with a visitor<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>management system and thereby free up time in the reception.&nbsp;</span></span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}">&nbsp;</span></p>
									<p><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}"><img src="https://www.goaskcody.com/hs-fs/hubfs/eBooks/Optimize%20front%20desk%20resources.png?t=1539679030137&amp;width=654&amp;height=436&amp;name=Optimize%20front%20desk%20resources.png" alt="Optimize front desk resources.png" width="654" height="436" class="" srcset="https://www.goaskcody.com/hs-fs/hubfs/eBooks/Optimize%20front%20desk%20resources.png?t=1539679030137&amp;width=327&amp;height=218&amp;name=Optimize%20front%20desk%20resources.png 327w, https://www.goaskcody.com/hs-fs/hubfs/eBooks/Optimize%20front%20desk%20resources.png?t=1539679030137&amp;width=654&amp;height=436&amp;name=Optimize%20front%20desk%20resources.png 654w, https://www.goaskcody.com/hs-fs/hubfs/eBooks/Optimize%20front%20desk%20resources.png?t=1539679030137&amp;width=981&amp;height=654&amp;name=Optimize%20front%20desk%20resources.png 981w, https://www.goaskcody.com/hs-fs/hubfs/eBooks/Optimize%20front%20desk%20resources.png?t=1539679030137&amp;width=1308&amp;height=872&amp;name=Optimize%20front%20desk%20resources.png 1308w, https://www.goaskcody.com/hs-fs/hubfs/eBooks/Optimize%20front%20desk%20resources.png?t=1539679030137&amp;width=1635&amp;height=1090&amp;name=Optimize%20front%20desk%20resources.png 1635w, https://www.goaskcody.com/hs-fs/hubfs/eBooks/Optimize%20front%20desk%20resources.png?t=1539679030137&amp;width=1962&amp;height=1308&amp;name=Optimize%20front%20desk%20resources.png 1962w" sizes="(max-width: 654px) 100vw, 654px"></span></p>
									<h2>What you'll learn:</h2>
									<p><strong>This eBook shows you how to optimize resources at the front desk while providing a better experience for external guests. With a visitor management software you can:&nbsp;</strong><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}">&nbsp;</span></p>
									<ul>
										<li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span><span>Create a great first impression of your building / office</span></span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}">&nbsp;</span></li>
										<li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span><span>Improve security with digital solution</span></span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}">&nbsp;</span></li>
										<li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span><span>Allow self-</span></span><span><span>registration<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>and<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>i</span></span><span><span>nstant</span></span><span><span><span>&nbsp;</span>employee<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>notifi</span></span><span><span>cation&nbsp;</span></span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}">&nbsp;</span></li>
										<li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span><span>Ditch manual processes</span></span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}">&nbsp;</span></li>
										<li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span><span>Provide</span></span><span><span><span>&nbsp;</span>check-out by smartphone</span></span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}">&nbsp;</span></li>
										<li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span><span>Send text message to employee / host when the guest<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>ar</span></span><span><span>rive</span></span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}">&nbsp;</span></li>
										<li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span><span>Improve security by keeping track of all visitors</span></span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}">&nbsp;</span></li>
									</ul>
								<p><span><span>Download this FREE<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>eBook</span></span><span><span><span>&nbsp;</span>and<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>learn<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>about the<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>11 ways visitor management<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>and office life is improved<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>with a virtual visitor management system integrated<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>into<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>you</span></span><span><span>r<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>Outlook and Office 365<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span>calenda</span></span><span><span>r.&nbsp;</span></span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}">&nbsp;</span></p></div>
							</div>
